    "@value" : "Overall MF required to adapt the variations of MF standards.  E.g., Japanese Maintenance Factor standard JIEG-001(2013) defines and uses “Ml”, “Md” instead of “LLMF”, “LSF”, “LMF”, “RSMF”. The Japanese MF Procedure is different from CIE 97:2005. Overall MF covers the difference."
